          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1595341607098-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Zest half your <strong>lime[s]</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Roll the<strong> lime[s]</strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
